  <entry>
    <title>搭建自己的个人博客(GitHub Pages+ Hexo)</title>
    <url>/2020-03-12-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2(GitHub%20Pages+%20Hexo).html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote class="blockquote-center">两天的学习，查了众多大佬的好文，整理出来，算对自己学习的一个总结。win10亲测。</blockquote>
<a id="more"></a>
<p><strong>注意：文中代码区皆在Git Bash中输入</strong></p>
<div class="note defalt no-icon">
            <h3 id="1-网页端"><a class="header-anchor" href="#1-网页端">¶</a>1 网页端</h3>
          </div>
<h4 id="1-1-注册GitHub账号"><a class="header-anchor" href="#1-1-注册GitHub账号">¶</a>1.1 注册GitHub账号</h4>
<h4 id="1-2-创建Your-username-github-io的Public仓库"><a class="header-anchor" href="#1-2-创建Your-username-github-io的Public仓库">¶</a>1.2 创建Your_username.github.io的Public仓库</h4>
<div class="note no-icon">
            <h3 id="2-本地端"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-本地端">¶</a>2 本地端</h3>
          </div>
<h4 id="2-1-环境配置"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-1-环境配置">¶</a>2.1 <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">环境配置</a></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://git-scm.com/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">安装Git</a></li>
<li><a href="https://nodejs.org/download/release/v10.24.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">安装Node.js</a>，一路下一步。</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="2-2-本地安装Hexo"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-2-本地安装Hexo">¶</a>2.2 本地安装Hexo</h4>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd d:/blog			# 或者右键文件夹根目录Git Bash </span><br><span class="line">npm i hexo-cli -g		# 安装Hexo</span><br><span class="line">Hexo -v				# 检查Hexo，显示版本号继续</span><br><span class="line">hexo init			# 初始化Hexo博客</span><br><span class="line">npm install			# 安装组件</span><br><span class="line">hexo g				# 生成静态网页</span><br><span class="line">hexo s				# 打开服务器，可以在http:<span class="comment">//localhost:4000/ 查看</span></span><br><span class="line">ctrl+c				# 关闭本地服务器</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>实现本地查看博客，jer动不？</p>
<h4 id="2-3-本地绑定GitHub"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-3-本地绑定GitHub">¶</a>2.3 本地绑定GitHub</h4>
<h5 id="2-3-1-第一种方法"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-3-1-第一种方法">¶</a>2.3.1 第一种方法</h5>
<p>找本机是否有ssh密钥</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/.ssh</span><br><span class="line">$ ls </span><br><span class="line">id_rsa known_hosts id_dsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>若有一对以 <code>id_rsa</code> 或 <code>id_rsa.pub</code> 命名的文件，则已有密钥。		<br>
若无，便建立密钥。（一路回车即可）</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ssh-keygen -o </span><br><span class="line">``` </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">打开github网站，登录后点击头像-settings，左侧SSH and GPG keys，新建一个SSH，名字随便，填入下面得到的SSH密码。</span><br><span class="line">```bash</span><br><span class="line">$ cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub </span><br><span class="line">ssh-rsa AAAA……@mylaptop.local</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>添加或更改密码</li>
</ul>
 <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ssh-keygen -p -f ~/.ssh/id_rsa</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h5 id="2-3-2-第二种方法"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-3-2-第二种方法">¶</a>2.3.2 第二种方法</h5>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">config</span> --global user.name <span class="string">"Your_username"</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">config</span> --global user.email <span class="string">"Your_email@qq.com"</span>   </span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"Your_email@qq.com"</span>		# 安装本地SSH</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Enter三连。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub		# 生成SSH密码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>打开github网站，登录后点击头像-settings，左侧SSH and GPG keys，新建一个SSH，名字随便，填入上步的得到的SSH密码。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>检测到用户名即为成功绑定。</p>
<h4 id="2-4-修改本地包上传目的地为GitHub"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-4-修改本地包上传目的地为GitHub">¶</a>2.4 修改本地包上传目的地为GitHub</h4>
<p>修改本地根目录文件_config.yml<br>
修改最后一行的配置为：</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: git@github.com:yourname/yourname.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>新版github博客只可显示master分支</p>
<img src="/2020-03-12-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2(GitHub%20Pages+%20Hexo)/settingsss.png" class="">
</blockquote>
<h4 id="2-5-调试"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-5-调试">¶</a>2.5 调试</h4>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g				# 生成静态网页</span><br><span class="line">hexo s				# 打开服务器，可以在http:<span class="comment">//localhost:4000/ 查看</span></span><br><span class="line">ctrl+c				# 关闭本地服务器</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="note success">
            <h4 id="2-6-第一次上传"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-6-第一次上传">¶</a>2.6 第一次上传</h4>
          </div>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save	#上传插件，自动装入package.json文件中</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean				#清缓存</span><br><span class="line">hexo g					#生成静态网页</span><br><span class="line">hexo d					#上传到GitHub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>💥上传完毕后，浏览器访问https://github.com/Your_username/Your_username.github.io 即可查看你的博客了。</strong></p>
<h4 id="2-7-写博文"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-7-写博文">¶</a>2.7 写博文</h4>
<p>直接在/source/_posts添加.md文件,需要用markdown语法编辑好后保存。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Win下Markdown软件推荐<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VScode</a>，是不是有点屈才？附<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/huyong/p/4573041.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1分钟VScode入门</a>以及<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/191d1e21f7ed" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1分钟markdown语法学习</a>。</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="2-8-跨电脑修改博客"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-8-跨电脑修改博客">¶</a>2.8 跨电脑修改博客</h4>
<p>创建分支hexo用于保存源文件，并在Github网站上设置为默认Branch，但设置中Page应为master分支。<br>
需要用Git把线上包下载到本地，链接最好采用SSH链接，使用如下命令：</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone git@github.com:Your-username/Your-username.github.io.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>之后在本地修改，再使用VScode上传源码后hexo编译即可。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i hexo-cli -g		# 安装Hexo</span><br><span class="line">Hexo -v				# 检查Hexo，显示版本号继续</span><br><span class="line">npm install			# 安装组件</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="note info">
            <h3 id="还有一点点"><a class="header-anchor" href="#还有一点点">¶</a>还有一点点</h3>
          </div>
<h4 id="Hexo技巧"><a class="header-anchor" href="#Hexo技巧">¶</a><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo技巧</a></h4>
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/asset-folders.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">添加图片</a></p>
<p>使用自带的相对路径引用标签插件<code>{% asset_img example.jpg This is an example image %}</code></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://kinboyw.github.io/2018/10/29/Hexo-NexT-%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF-emoji/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">添加支持emoji</a></p>
<p>采用hexo-renderer-markdown-it插件代替hexo-renderer-markdown</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="更换博客模板—推荐Next模板"><a class="header-anchor" href="#更换博客模板—推荐Next模板">¶</a>更换博客模板—推荐<a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Next</a>模板</h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://theme-next.org/docs/getting-started/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Next官方主题配置</a> 、<a href="https://guanqr.com/tech/website/hexo-theme-next-customization/#top" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Next民间个性化</a></li>
</ul>
